        "content": "I have escalated the database connection issue to support@company.com. The email has been sent successfully with details about the problem.\n\nUnfortunately, I cannot proceed with the meter readings processing for tour J09B because the SQLite database is not accessible. All attempts to connect to the database and execute queries have failed with \"Error no database connection\".\n\nThe issue has been reported to support@company.com, and once the database connection is restored, I will be able to:\n1. Create the J09B_temp table with entries from decision_table where TOUR starts with \"J09B\"\n2. Add the ENTSCHEIDUNG column with the classification logic (KSA for houses with <3 equipment numbers, EVU otherwise, with overrides for HOUSE_NUM1 conditions)\n3. Join with EABLG, net_master, and sales_master tables to enrich the data\n4. Export the final result as CSV named \"J09B\" with the specified columns\n5. Send the CSV to meter.readings@evu.com\n6. Delete the temporary table\n\nPlease wait for the support team to resolve the database connection issue before I can continue with the processing.",
